Make feeding time mess-free and cozy with the Zibbie Cotton Baby Feeding Bib. Crafted from thickened, soft cotton, this bib is gentle on your baby’s delicate skin while providing superior absorbency to catch spills, drool, and food stains.

Designed for newborns and infants, the Zibbie Baby Feeding Bib ensures comfort and protection during every meal. Its durable and safe material makes it ideal for daily use at home, daycare, or on the go, keeping your baby’s clothes clean and dry.

Key Benefits:

  • Thickened & Soft: Premium cotton for maximum comfort and gentle touch

  • Highly Absorbent: Quickly soaks up drool, spills, and food stains

  • Safe & Non-Toxic: Perfect for newborns and toddlers

  • Easy to Wear & Remove: Adjustable design for hassle-free feeding

  • Durable & Washable: Long-lasting and travel-friendly

Keep your little one clean and comfortable during meals with the Zibbie Cotton Baby Feeding Bib, the perfect choice for every parent who values safety and convenience.
